import React from 'react'
import {Nav, NavbarContainer} from './Navbar.elements'

const Navbar = () => {
    return (
        <>
         <Nav>
            <NavbarContainer>
                <NavLogo to="/">
                    <NavIcon />
                    UpperStairs
                </NavLogo>
            </NavbarContainer>
         </Nav>            
        </>
    )
}

export default Navbar
